text: HD 191806 is an 8th magnitude K-type star located approximately 226 light years away in the constellation Cygnus. In 2016, a massive gas giant planet was found in orbit around the star. == See also == * List of extrasolar planets == References == Category:K-type main-sequence stars 191806 099306 Category:Durchmusterung objects Category:Cygnus (constellation) Category:Planetary systems with one confirmed planet
